'''沃森综合征'''（'''Watson syndrome'''）是一种[[常染色体|常染色体]][[显性遗传|显性]][[遗传病|遗传病]]。以[[虹膜色素缺陷瘤|虹膜色素缺陷瘤]]、[[腋窝|腋窝]]/[[腹股沟|腹股沟]]斑点和[[神经纤维瘤|神经纤维瘤]]形成为特点<ref name="Bolognia">{{cite book |author=Rapini, Ronald P.; Bolognia, Jean L.; Jorizzo, Joseph L. |title=Dermatology: 2-Volume Set |publisher=Mosby |location=St. Louis |year=2007 |pages=725,831 |isbn=1-4160-2999-0 |oclc= |doi= |accessdate=}}</ref>。

沃森综合征可能和引起[[Ⅰ型神经纤维瘤病|Ⅰ型神经纤维瘤病]]的[[神经纤维瘤蛋白1|神经纤维瘤蛋白1]]拥有相同的[[等位基因|等位基因]]<ref>{{cite journal |author=Allanson JE, Upadhyaya M, Watson GH, ''et al.'' |title=Watson syndrome: is it a subtype of type 1 neurofibromatosis? |journal=J. Med. Genet. |volume=28 |issue=11 |pages=752–6 |pmid=1770531 |pmc=1017110 |doi=10.1136/jmg.28.11.752 |url=http://jmg.bmj.com/content/28/11/752.full.pdf |format=PDF |date=November 1991 |access-date=2011-12-02 |archive-date=2012-03-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120320120123/http://jmg.bmj.com/content/28/11/752.full.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

